B.QG=new A.dY("Policy text contrast below minimum threshold","Secondary text used for exclusion notes and footnotes rendered at approximately 3.2:1 against the card background. Users with moderate visual impairment would struggle to read this at a key decision point.",B.ea,"1.4.3 Contrast (Minimum)","Text token updated from the legacy muted grey to a value passing 4.5:1 on all background colours used in the flow.")
B.QD=new A.dY("Accordion expand controls not keyboard accessible","Policy detail accordions could not be expanded via keyboard alone. Users navigating without a mouse had no access to the content hidden behind them.",B.ea,"2.1.1 Keyboard","Keyboard accessibility restored by ensuring MudExpansionPanel received focus correctly and responded to Enter and Space.")
B.QL=new A.dY("Tooltip-only disclosure of exclusion detail","Several exclusion items showed their full description only on hover via a tooltip, with no fallback for touch or keyboard users.",B.d9,"1.3.3 Sensory Characteristics / 2.1.1 Keyboard","Redesign moves exclusion detail into inline expandable rows accessible regardless of input method.")
B.QB=new A.dY("CTA button label does not describe the action clearly","The primary action button read \u201cContinue\u201d with no context. Screen reader users navigating by button had no indication of what they were continuing to.",B.d9,"2.4.6 Headings and Labels","Button label revised to \u201cContinue to payment\u201d with aria-describedby linking to a brief summary of the selected policy.")
B.QI=new A.dY("No visible focus ring on interactive elements","Focus outlines were suppressed globally in the component library configuration, making it impossible to track keyboard position across the entire flow.",B.d9,"2.4.7 Focus Visible","MudBlazor focus styles re-enabled and customised to use the brand accent colour at 2px width, passing 3:1 contrast against all backgrounds.")
B.QH=new A.dY("Page title does not reflect the current step","The document title remained \u201cPerfect Pet Insurance\u201d throughout the multi-step flow with no indication of the current stage.",B.ja,"2.4.2 Page Titled","Title updated to include the current step: \u201cReview your policy \u2014 Perfect Pet Insurance\u201d.")
