B.Io=s(["Internal testing suggested the revised flow was easier to understand and felt more credible, particularly in terms of readability, structure, and the reduction of visual inconsistency.","The redesigned Review Details experience is now scheduled for A/B testing in Amplitude alongside live traffic, to measure its impact on conversion and engagement metrics.","A parallel segment of the redesigned quote flow was already deployed and tested with real users during this project. Learnings from that experiment \u2014 around visual density, information ordering, and reassurance \u2014 directly shaped the decisions made here.","Once the A/B experiment has run long enough to produce reliable findings, this case study will be updated with completion rate data and any broader changes in user behaviour.","The most important takeaway: improving visual polish alone would not have moved the needle. The meaningful change came from reducing the cognitive effort required for users to understand what they were reviewing and feel confident enough to proceed."],t.s)
